	   <tr><td colspan=2>Short and sweet:&nbsp;&nbsp;200 is the soft cap for Wis/Int for casters.  This means you gain the full benefit of each point until 200 (which is about 10 mana per point at level 50), but each point after 200 gives a much lower value for mana.  The current speculation is every point over 200 gives 1 mana.<br><br>Gorthin Spiritcaller<br>51 Shaman BB<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
