	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another suggestion, if you HAVE to run thru FV to bank or whatever, use SoW...not Scale of Wolf.&nbsp;&nbsp; Using Scale, if one of those pesky bugs hits you, your Scale pops off, then no way are you going to outrun them.<br><br>AND...now with the new line of translocate spells for wizards, getting a ride somewhere is easier than ever.  If you need to bank and don't want to make the run to FV, just make sure you are bound in Windmill (or somewhere else in LoIO), and seek out a TL to Gfay.  The spires there are close to Felwithe bank.  Do your banking, buy food, sell  your loot, then gate back to LoIO.<br>&nbsp;<br>Badjur<br>Oracle of Novus Invictus<br>(Druzzil Ro)<br><br>Aepox Weeblatter<br>51 Dwarf Warrior</td></tr>
