	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.65]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>On the docks in FV, last building on your right on your way off the dock (it's the only building on the docks a barb can actually walk into).&nbsp;&nbsp; Walk straight into the building and it will be the second merchant on your right.  Scale of Wolf is one of the bottom spells in this merchant's inventory, so do not be discouraged if you check one of the top spells and find lvl 50+ spells.  Scale IS there :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Badjur<br>Oracle of Novus Invictus<br>(Druzzil Ro)<br><br>Aepox Weeblatter<br>51 Dwarf Warrior</td></tr>
